    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nThe feature request is related to the integration of Hudi (Apache Hudi) with Spark Rapids. Currently, Hudi is not supported in Spark Rapids, and I would like to request the addition of this feature.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nHudi table read and write support is need on Spark RAPIDS\r\n\r\n- [ ] Hudi table read operation (spark DF and spark sql read )\r\n- [ ] Hudi table optimised writes operation (spark DF and spark sql write)\r\n- [ ] MERGE INTO table feature for Hudi\r\n- [ ] Append command feature for Hudi\r\n- [ ] Delete command feature for Hudi\r\n- [ ] Update command feature in Hudi\r\n- [ ] Overwrite command feature in Hudi\r\n- [ ] Hudi table auto compaction",
